text.text: It was so much fun! The kitties are very cute and the staff here is so nice! And they have an amazing menu of drinks! And it's neatly set up! I definitely recommend coming here!

What can I say? This cafe has everything that I wish I could have had when I was growing up. A safe, inclusive space to come and simply be with the added benefit of the therapy that calming kitties can bring. All of the staff are insanely sweet, and I love talking to them when things are quiet. Even talking to other patrons coming by about the cafe, about the town, it's a wonderful and peaceful atmosphere and meeting spot.

You can also bring your own games to the location to play on their retro consoles, and honestly it's one of my fave parts. Being able to play then take a break to watch the kittens play while I have a snack and drink some lotus? Hell yeah!

Highly recommended for dates, gatherings, and overall just to support the cause!
(This is also my advertisement for someone to adopt Bean Dip/Chip or as I like to call him Beanie Baby ü•∞ sweetest little black kitten!)

The atmosphere and the people here are so very friendly! And the kittens are to cute! The drinks are very refreshing and if you ever need a place to calm or mind or to get away‚Ä¶ this is the place!  I highly recommend.

cafes.address: 312 5th St, West Des Moines, IA 50265, USA

text.text: Service was excellent. Cats were cats! Fun to sit with. Really liked the staff that politely told a customer, that was not taking the hint from the cat, she did not like pets! Drinks were good!

Love cats? Love coffee? Art? Look no further for your heaven! Yoga with cats a couple times a week, come to hang out with cats, drink excellent lattes, have a pastry (gluten-free available), grab some grab and go lunch items and hang out! The vibes are good, authentic, and fun. There are tons of original art items for sale too!
Such a fun place with a great cause! We enjoyed specialty coffees that were hot and flavorful while experiencing the cat room. Staff were friendly and knowledgeable. üêà‚òïÔ∏èüò∫
